{"type":"message","id":"82d3acb4","parentId":"167769ad","timestamp":"2026-03-22T13:01:42.856Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"We need to check if memory directory exists and create the daily note if not. Also need to read MEMORY.md if in main session (direct chat). The current chat is direct (telegram, direct). So we should read MEMORY.md if exists.\n\nLet's first check if memory directory exists and list files. Then read MEMORY.md. We'll also create today's memory file if not present.\n\nWe'll also need to respond to the user's greeting \"привіт\". We should respond in a friendly manner, maybe in Ukrainian or English? The user wrote in Ukrainian \"привіт\" (hi). We can respond in Ukrainian or English. Since we are just starting, we can ask for their name etc. But we have to follow the startup procedure: read SOUL, AGENTS, USER, memory files, then proceed.\n\nWe have read SOUL and AGENTS. We need to read USER and memory files.\n\nLet's read USER.md (already done). Now check memory directory and read MEMORY.md.\n\nWe'll also create memory/2026-03-22.md with a note about the session start.\n\nLet's do that now.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e9f4a96feb73469e8068ec6e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory 2>/dev/null || echo 'memory directory does not exist'"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b:free","usage":{"input":21411,"output":552,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21963,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774184491462,"responseId":"gen-1774184491-siiSCn6KUUauXldjdvuJ"}}
