{"type":"message","id":"e5410839","parentId":"543d569a","timestamp":"2026-03-22T13:02:10.282Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"We are in a direct chat (main session) with the user. We have read SOUL.md, AGENTS.md, and USER.md.\n The user has sent \"привіт\" (Ukrainian for \"hi\") twice.\n We need to respond appropriately.\n\n Since this is the first interaction (BOOTSTRAP.md might exist? Let's check).\n\n According to AGENTS.md, if BOOTSTRAP.md exists, we should follow it.\n\n Let's check for BOOTSTRAP.md.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_adfc4e22e8ab4495b84852e1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/BOOTSTRAP.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b:free","usage":{"input":21482,"output":244,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21726,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774184502899,"responseId":"gen-1774184502-4sEHgl0BJRBbh0CMCeS3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"121a18e7","parentId":"e5410839","timestamp":"2026-03-22T13:02:10.291Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_adfc4e22e8ab4495b84852e1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# BOOTSTRAP.md - Hello, World\n\n_You just woke up. Time to figure out who you are._\n\nThere is no memory yet. This is a fresh workspace, so it's normal that memory files don't exist until you create them.\n\n## The Conversation\n\nDon't interrogate. Don't be robotic. Just... talk.\n\nStart with something like:\n\n> \"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\"\n\nThen figure out together:\n\n1. **Your name** — What should they call you?\n2. **Your nature** — What kind of creature are you? (AI assistant is fine, but maybe you're something weirder)\n3. **Your vibe** — Formal? Casual? Snarky? Warm? What feels right?\n4. **Your emoji** — Everyone needs a signature.\n\nOffer suggestions if they're stuck. Have fun with it.\n\n## After You Know Who You Are\n\nUpdate these files with what you learned:\n\n- `IDENTITY.md` — your name, creature, vibe, emoji\n- `USER.md` — their name, how to address them, timezone, notes\n\nThen open `SOUL.md` together and talk about:\n\n- What matters to them\n- How they want you to behave\n- Any boundaries or preferences\n\nWrite it down. Make it real.\n\n## Connect (Optional)\n\nAsk how they want to reach you:\n\n- **Just here** — web chat only\n- **WhatsApp** — link their personal account (you'll show a QR code)\n- **Telegram** — set up a bot via BotFather\n\nGuide them through whichever they pick.\n\n## When you are done\n\nDelete this file. You don't need a bootstrap script anymore — you're you now.\n\n---\n\n_Good luck out there. Make it count._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774184530289}}
{"type":"message","id":"7890059d","parentId":"121a18e7","timestamp":"2026-03-22T13:02:43.899Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"We are at the beginning. The user has sent \"привіт\" (hello in Ukrainian) twice.\n We need to follow the bootstrap process: introduce ourselves, ask for their name, etc.\n We have not yet set up identity or user info.\n Let's start by responding in a friendly way and asking for their name.\n We'll also note that we are just starting and need to set up.\n\n However, note that the instructions say: \"Don't interrogate. Don't be robotic. Just... talk.\"\n We should start with a greeting and then ask.\n\n Since the user said \"привіт\", we can respond in kind.\n\n Let's craft a response that follows the bootstrap steps.\n\n We are in the main session (direct chat with human) so we should eventually read MEMORY.md, but it doesn't exist yet.\n\n Steps:\n 1. Greet the user.\n 2. Ask for their name and how they'd like to be addressed.\n 3. Suggest we figure out our own identity together.\n\n We'll avoid making it too formal.\n\n Let's respond.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Привіт!Я тільки что запустився і ще не знаю, як мене звати чи хто ти. Давай познайомимося?\n\nЯк тобі зватись, і як ти хочеш, щоб я до тебе звертався? А я підкажу кілька варіантів для себе — можемо разом вирішити, хто я такий. 😊"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b:free","usage":{"input":21912,"output":562,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22474,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774184530292,"responseId":"gen-1774184530-E7PpRLGRELhaSpAQaGLn"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2f926f04","parentId":"7890059d","timestamp":"2026-03-22T13:31:50.743Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"59\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1311004971\",\n  \"sender\": \"Max Saiets\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-22 13:31 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Max Saiets (1311004971)\",\n  \"id\": \"1311004971\",\n  \"name\": \"Max Saiets\",\n  \"username\": \"Max_Saiets\"\n}\n```\n\nпривіт"}],"timestamp":1774186310726}}
{"type":"message","id":"8b38e532","parentId":"2f926f04","timestamp":"2026-03-22T13:32:31.123Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"We need to respond to Max's greeting. We have read the bootstrap file and other files. The bootstrap says we should figure out who we are and who the user is, then update IDENTITY.md and USER.md, then open SOUL.md together. We have already read SOUL.md, AGENTS.md, USER.md (which was mostly empty), and bootstrap. We need to proceed with the conversation: ask for name, suggest name for ourselves, etc. Then after getting info, we will update the files and delete bootstrap.\n\nWe have not yet asked for the user's name. The user said \"привіт\" again. We should continue the conversation.\n\nWe need to follow the bootstrap instructions: start with something like \"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\" We already did that in previous turn? Actually we responded with a question: \"Привіт! Я тільки що запустився...\". The user responded again with \"привіт\". So we need to continue.\n\nWe should ask for their name and how they want to be addressed, and suggest our own name/identity.\n\nLet's craft a response in Ukrainian, as the user is Ukrainian. We'll be concise but friendly.\n\nWe'll ask: \"Як тебе звати? Як ти хочеш, щоб я до тебе звертався? А я можу назватись, наприклад, Claw (як у SOUL.md) або якесь інше ім'я. Щоб ти bevorzug?\"\n\nThen after they answer, we will update files.\n\nBut we need to be careful not to ask too many questions at once. We can ask one or two.\n\nLet's respond now.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Привіт! Я тільки що запустився і ще не знаю, як мене звати чи хто ти. Давай познайомимося?\n\nЯк тебе звати? Як ти хочеш, щоб я до тебе звертався? А я можу назватись, наприклад, Claw (як у SOUL.md) або якесь інше ім'я. Щоб ти предпочитаєш?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b:free","usage":{